    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce the period penalty points are on a licence for driving without insurance",
        "additional_details": "Having points on your licence can make it difficult to get a job that involves driving a motor vehicle, and we think the current rules are too strict, and should be changed for this offence.",
        "background": "I want the Government to reduce the length of time penalty points are on a driver's licence for the offence of driving without valid insurance.",
